latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The low down on keratin hair treatment from a dermatologist. 

The question of whether or not to do it, is entirely up to you. There is definitely damage to your hair, as well as a few side effects as I have mentioned in the video above. But some people don't mind taking on the risks for that gorgeous shine and smooth texture, despite the downside. I have made an attempt to help you make an informed decision on it, so you know what you're getting into.

latestPosts.caption:
Storytime: Sana had been struggling with cystic acne for years, breakouts that wouldn’t budge, flare-ups that left her feeling helpless, and skin that just didn’t feel like her own. 

She tried it all, home remedies, over-the-counter products, even trending skincare. Nothing worked. Until she reached out for an online consultation.

We kept it simple but powerful, no gimmicks, just science-backed, medical-grade skincare customized to her skin’s exact needs.
& yes not in-clinic treatments. No filters. Just the right products, right routine, and the right guidance.

Over a few months, her skin transformed and so did her confidence.

If you’ve been stuck in a cycle of trial and error, remember this: you don’t need more products. You need what’s right for you.

Big credit to @sana_un_suna for talking aloud about her journey- it’s not always easy. She encouraged me to share her story so it could help more people! 

DM for consultations or just to talk & we’re here to guide you, not sell to you. 🤝
